Jan (https://github.com/menloresearch/jan)
Copyright (c) Menlo Research Inc.
License: Apache-2.0

Used by: Plugsky Desktop (desktop/install)
The Plugsky Desktop installer downloads and embeds the Jan binary (a native
AI chat client) as a private runtime at `~/.plugsky-desktop/.runtime/`. We
patch the macOS Info.plist to set CFBundleName, CFBundleDisplayName,
CFBundleExecutable, and CFBundleIdentifier to Plugsky branding strings, and
re-sign the bundle ad-hoc. The Jan application code itself is unmodified.

The full Apache-2.0 license for Jan is available at:
https://github.com/menloresearch/jan/blob/main/LICENSE

