Copyright (c) 2023- Open WebUI Inc.
License: Open WebUI License (custom, see link below)

Used by: Plugsky Web (desktop/openwebui/install)
The Plugsky Web installer pulls the official Open WebUI Docker image (Docker
backend) or runs the official open-webui pip package (pip backend), unmodified.
Plugsky branding lives in the shim command name (plugsky-web), the default
model and API URL config in ~/.plugsky-web/.env, and accompanying
documentation. The Open WebUI application code, name, and visual identifiers
remain unmodified per the Open WebUI License's branding clause.

